{
  "id": "RAW_d21cfda4",
  "title": "T5Gemma 2：下一代编码器-解码器模型",
  "url": "https://blog.google/technology/developers/t5gemma-2/",
  "date": "2025-12-18 18:34:28",
  "author": "Biao Zhang",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"T5Gemma 2: The next generation of encoder\\u002Ddecoder models\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-12-18T18:34:28.666285+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;T5Gemma 2: The next generation of encoder\\u002Ddecoder models&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"7j9y9\" class=\"drop-cap\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.14856\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">T5Gemma 2</a> is the next evolution of our encoder-decoder family based on Gemma 3, featuring the first multi-modal and long-context encoder-decoder models.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"d5qcc\">Unlike T5Gemma, T5Gemma 2 adopts tied word embeddings (over encoder and decoder) and merged decoder self- and cross-attention to save model parameters. It offers compact pre-trained models at sizes of 270M-270M (~370M total, excluding vision encoder), 1B-1B (~1.7B) and 4B-4B (~7B) parameters, making them ideal for rapid experimentation and deployment in on-device applications.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"amrfl\">Background</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"f86n5\">With the original <a href=\"https://developers.googleblog.com/en/t5gemma/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">T5Gemma</a>, we demonstrated that we could successfully adapt modern, pre-trained decoder-only models into an encoder-decoder architecture, unlocking new versatility. By initializing with weights from a powerful decoder-only model and then applying continued pre-training, we created high-quality, inference-efficient models while bypassing the computational cost of training from scratch.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"fljar\">T5Gemma 2 extends this into the realm of vision-language models by incorporating key innovations from Gemma 3.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"dlcqj\">What’s new</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"3mg06\">T5Gemma 2 is more than a re-training. It incorporates significant architectural changes while inheriting many of the powerful, next-generation features of the Gemma 3 family.</p>\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"2sigb\">Architectural innovations for efficiency</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"djbnv\">To maximize efficiency at smaller scales, we have introduced key structural refinements:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"8jb3m\"><b>Tied embeddings:</b> We now tie the embeddings between the encoder and decoder. This significantly reduces the overall parameter count, allowing us to pack more active capabilities into the same memory footprint — crucial for our new compact 270M-270M model.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"81pdv\"><b>Merged attention:</b> In the decoder, we adopt a merged attention mechanism, combining self- and cross-attention into a single, unified attention layer. This reduces model parameters and architectural complexity, improving model parallelization and benefiting inference.</li>\n     </ul>\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"c6ibb\">Next-generation capabilities</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2ls8k\">Drawing from Gemma 3, T5Gemma 2 also represents a significant upgrade in model capabilities:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"cln6a\"><b>Multimodality:</b> T5Gemma 2 models can understand and process images alongside text. By utilizing a highly efficient vision encoder, the models can seamlessly perform visual question answering and multimodal reasoning tasks.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"7b1hr\"><b>Extended long context:</b> We've dramatically expanded the context window. Leveraging Gemma 3's alternating local and global attention mechanism, T5Gemma 2 can handle context windows of up to 128K tokens.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"f1t8a\"><b>Massively multilingual:</b> Trained on a larger, more diverse dataset, these models now support over 140 languages out of the box.</li>\n     </ul>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"6i3nf\">Performance</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"efjl4\">T5Gemma 2 sets a new standard for what compact encoder-decoder models can achieve. Our new models demonstrate strong performance across key capability areas, inheriting the powerful multimodal and long-context features from the Gemma 3 architecture.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"T5Gemma 2: The next generation of encoder\\u002Ddecoder models\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1a_rEj400Y.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1a_rEj400Y.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Stem and Code Bar Chart 1&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1b_NoaRso0.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1b_NoaRso0.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Reasoning and Factuality Bar Chart 1&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1c_4TfnVTY.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1c_4TfnVTY.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Multilingual Bar Chart 1&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1d_udeLl71.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1d_udeLl71.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Multimodal Bar Chart 1&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1e_FexKBEb.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1e_FexKBEb.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Long Context Bar Chart 1&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;T5Gemma 2: The next generation of encoder\\\\u002Ddecoder models&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1766088312729\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 267.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1766088312729-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 5\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1a_rEj400Y.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1a_rEj400Y.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"Stem and Code Bar Chart 1\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1a_rEj400Y.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312729-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312729-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312729-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312729-3\" data-index=\"4\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312729-4\" data-index=\"5\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 5</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;T5Gemma 2: The next generation of encoder\\u002Ddecoder models&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"7j9y9\"><i>Pre-training performance of Gemma 3, T5Gemma and T5Gemma 2 across five unique capabilities.</i></p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"d6lo1\">As shown in the charts above, T5Gemma 2 delivers:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"ig02\"><b>Strong multimodal performance</b>, outperforming Gemma 3 on several benchmarks. We adapt text-only Gemma 3 base models (270M and 1B) into effective multimodal encoder-decoder models.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"c9e34\"><b>Superior long-context capability</b>, with substantial quality gains over Gemma 3 and T5Gemma. Using a separate encoder makes T5Gemma 2 better at handling long-context problems.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"8d2dk\"><b>Improved general capabilities</b>. Across coding, reasoning and multilingual tasks, T5Gemma 2 generally surpasses its corresponding Gemma 3 counterpart.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"T5Gemma 2: The next generation of encoder\\u002Ddecoder models\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2a_ujNUT3c.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2a_ujNUT3c.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Stem and Code Bar Chart 2&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2b_FTIWGlT.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2b_FTIWGlT.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Reasoning and Factuality Bar Chart 2&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2c_sT6yU5w.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2c_sT6yU5w.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Multilingual Bar Chart 2&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2d_lLPQSDG.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2d_lLPQSDG.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Multimodal Bar Chart 2&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2e_noRgImg.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2e_noRgImg.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Long Context Bar Chart 2&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;T5Gemma 2: The next generation of encoder\\\\u002Ddecoder models&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1766088312731\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 267.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1766088312731-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 5\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2a_ujNUT3c.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2a_ujNUT3c.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"Stem and Code Bar Chart 2\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/2a_ujNUT3c.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$866076223$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312731-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312731-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312731-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312731-3\" data-index=\"4\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1766088312731-4\" data-index=\"5\"><!--?lit$866076223$-->Jump to position 5</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;T5Gemma 2: The next generation of encoder\\u002Ddecoder models&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"7j9y9\"><i>Post-training performance.</i> <i>Note: we are not releasing any post-trained / IT checkpoints. These results here are only for illustration, where we performed a minimal SFT without RL for T5Gemma 2. Also note pre-training and post-training benchmarks are different, so scores are not comparable across plots.</i></p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"8rk3r\">Similar to the original T5Gemma, we find that the post-training performance of T5Gemma 2 generally yields better results than its decoder-only counterparts. This makes T5Gemma 2 suitable for both large language model research as well as downstream applications.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"9kp0s\">Getting started</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"c0599\">We’re looking forward to seeing what the community builds with T5Gemma 2. This release includes pre-trained checkpoints, designed to be post-trained by developers for specific tasks before deployment.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"1jig8\">These pre-trained checkpoints are available now for broad use across several platforms:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"2tb99\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.14856\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Read the paper on arXiv</b></a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"6f6t2\"><a href=\"https://www.kaggle.com/models/google/t5gemma-2\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Download on Kaggle</b></a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"a01iv\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/collections/google/t5gemma-2\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Available on Hugging Face</b></a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"fqg6k\"><a href=\"https://colab.research.google.com/github/google-gemini/gemma-cookbook/blob/main/Research/[T5Gemma_2]Example.ipynb\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Explore via Colab</b></a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"4jh5a\"><a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/publishers/google/model-garden/t5gemma\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Run Inference via Vertex AI<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></b></a></li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌推出 T5Gemma 2，作为基于 Gemma 3 构建的新一代紧凑型、多模态、长上下文编码器-解码器模型，为多种应用带来更高的效率和卓越的性能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌推出 T5Gemma 2，作为基于 Gemma 3 构建的新一代紧凑型、多模态、长上下文编码器-解码器模型，为多种应用带来更高的效率和卓越的性能。",
  "summary": "本文宣布发布 T5Gemma 2，这是谷歌编码器-解码器模型系列的演进，融合了 Gemma 3 的创新成果。其主要特点包括架构效率提升，例如词嵌入共享和融合注意力机制，这些显著减少了参数数量和复杂性，使得模型更加紧凑（参数规模从约 3.7 亿到约 70 亿不等）。T5Gemma 2 继承了 Gemma 3 的先进功能，如多模态处理（支持图像和文本）、长达 128K 词元的扩展上下文窗口，以及对 140 多种语言的广泛多语言支持。性能基准测试显示，T5Gemma 2 在多模态、长上下文、编码、推理和多语言任务方面均优于 Gemma 3 和 T5Gemma，使其成为大型语言模型（LLM）研究和下游应用的有力竞争者。这些模型目前可通过 arXiv、Kaggle、Hugging Face、Colab 和 Vertex AI 获取。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "T5Gemma 2 引入了架构创新，以提升效率和紧凑性。",
      "explanation": "通过采用词嵌入共享和融合注意力机制，T5Gemma 2 大幅减少了参数数量和架构复杂性，非常适合紧凑部署和快速实验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该模型继承了 Gemma 3 的下一代能力，包括多模态和扩展长上下文。",
      "explanation": "T5Gemma 2 能够无缝处理图像和文本，支持高达 128K 词元的上下文窗口，并支持 140 多种语言，极大地拓展了其应用范围。"
    },
    {
      "point": "与前几代相比，T5Gemma 2 在关键能力上表现出卓越性能。",
      "explanation": "基准测试显示，T5Gemma 2 在多模态、长上下文、编码、推理和多语言任务方面，性能超越了前几代模型 Gemma 3 和 T5Gemma，为紧凑型编码器-解码器模型树立了新标准。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "T5Gemma 2 是我们基于 Gemma 3 的编码器-解码器系列的最新演进，首次引入了多模态和长上下文编码器-解码器模型。",
